<p>I am currently a Ph.D. student at the University of Exeter. I have also spent half a year in London at the Alan Turing Institute as an <a href="https://www.turing.ac.uk/people/jin-wang">enrichment student</a>. My research interest includes cloud and edge computing, learning-based system optimisation, reinforcement learning, and applied machine learning.</p>

<p>I received both of my B.S. and M.S. from University of Electronic Science and Technology of China (UESTC), majored in Computer Science.</p>

